                                        <p>The Trustees wish to have at least 8,000 acres and with a minimum Capital Account balance of $10,000,000.00 at the time of expiration. The Capital Account Minimum will ensure further benefit to the Tribal Members after expiration. Once the minimum threshold is met, the Trustees wish to use strictly interest for additional purchases.</p>

