                                        <h2>High School Academic Incentive Policy</h2>
                                        
                                        <div class="divider divider-center"><i class="icon-circle"></i></div>
                                        <h2>Rationale for Revision</h2>
                                        
                                        <p>There has been a major challenge in awarding the incentive because different high schools do not report monthly attendance updates. This compromises the accountability procedure when there is no paperwork.</p>
                                        
                                        <p>Effective September, 2014, the incentive program will be based on academic merit for each school year.  Incentive will not be issued on a monthly basis.</p>
                                        
                                        <p>The incentive will be available to on-reserve/off reserve students who are in grades 9 to grade 12.  It will be $50.00 per credit earned or course passed during the ten month school year.  Students will be awarded the monetary incentive after the first semester and at the end of the school year based on their transcript</p>
                                        
                                        <p>Students must provide their report cards/transcript to Director of Education or designate.  These can be:</p>
                                        
                                        <ul>
                                        
                                            <li>
                                                <p>Mailed to Box 430, Portage la Prairie MB   R1N 3B7</p>
                                            </li>
                                            
                                            <li>
                                                <p>Faxed to 1-204-252-2012</p>
                                            </li>
                                            
                                            <li>
                                                <p>Emailed to or dropped off at the Administration Building</p>
                                            </li>
                                            
                                            
                                        </ul>
                                        
                                        <p>Cheques will be mailed to off-reserve high school students.  On-reserve high school students can pick theirs up at the administration building.  There will be a $75.00 Christmas incentive for any student who is registered in grade 9 to grade 12 on December 1st.</p>
                                        
